    <text id="A7553T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Evans writes briefly to report on family news and send his love.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-03-17">March 17 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>My Dear Mollie</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>We all rived home Safely we had a very warm ride it felt like August. I was very
                    sorry I did not Stay <orig reg="until">untill</orig> Evening with you I wish you
                    had of <orig reg="mentioned">menchend</orig> it to me when your Pa Started I
                    thought I had to go <orig reg="too">two</orig> I wished often on my way home I
                    had Stayed with you <orig reg="until">untill</orig> Evening. your Pa did not
                    Start to Baltimore this morning but will leave Tomorrow. Ada says She <orig
                        reg="don't">dont</orig> want to go to Gordonsville She<pb n="2"/>wanted me
                    to take her back home I told her that she had started &amp; that her Pa
                    would not let her go back he told her if She did not like it She could come on
                    to Baltimore &amp; Stay with him.</p>

                <p>I wish I was with you <orig reg="today">to day</orig> I would then be happy I
                    love you Truly &amp; devotedly my only &amp; greatest <orig
                        reg="pleasure">plesure</orig> is to be with you who I love with all The
                        <orig reg="Strength">Strenth</orig> &amp; devotion of my heart I love
                    you &amp; only you no woman in all This world can ever take my heart
                    &amp; all of its deep &amp; fervent love<pb n="3"/>from you. I know that
                    you have <orig reg="been">bin</orig> lonely Since we all left I do wish that
                    could have Stayed with you all This week I will be down Saturday week if I live</p>

                <p>you must Excuse this letter it was <orig reg="written">writin</orig> in haste as
                    I had but a few moments to write give my love to your Ma &amp; Ham all the
                    children</p>

                <p>I Send love &amp; a kiss to you write me a long letter Friday I love to read
                    them</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours</salute>
                    <signed>D H Evans</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
